the crash happened at about 14:15 bst on the b1191 at thornton, near woodhall spa.
lincolnshire police said the motorcyclist killed in the collision lived locally, but has not released any further details.
the tractor driver was not injured.
the force has appealed for witnesses to the collision to come forward.
the b1191 was closed in both directions between the b1192 tattershall road junction in woodhall spa and the a158 jubilee way junction in horncastle